    {
      "type": "texte",
      "value": "Simplifier au maximum les expressions complexes suivantes."
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "$\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)}{1+i}$"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "En multipliant numérateur et dénominateur par le conjugué du dénominateur :\n\t\t$$\n\t\t\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)}{1+i}=\\frac{(1+3 i)(3+i)(1-i)}{(1+i)(1-i)}=\\frac{10+10 i}{2}=5+5 i\n\t\t$$"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "$(1-i)^8$"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "On a $(1-i)^2=-2 i$. On en déduit :\n\t\t$$\n\t\t(1-i)^8=\\left((1-i)^2\\right)^4=(-2 i)^4=2^4 \\cdot i^4=16\n\t\t$$"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "$\\left(\\frac{1+i \\sqrt{3}}{1-i \\sqrt{3}}\\right)^5$"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "$$\\begin{align*}\n\t\t\t\\left(\\frac{1+i \\sqrt{3}}{1-i \\sqrt{3}}\\right)^5 & =\\left(\\frac{\\frac{1}{2}+\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}}{\\frac{1}{2}-\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}}\\right)^5 \\\\ &=\\left(\\frac{\\cos \\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)}{\\cos \\left(-\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(-\\frac{\\pi}{3}\\right)}\\right)^5 \\\\ &=\\left(\\frac{e^{i \\frac{\\pi}{3}}}{e^{-i \\frac{\\pi}{3}}}\\right)^5 \\\\ &=\\left(e^{i \\frac{2 \\pi}{3}}\\right)^5=e^{i \\frac{10 \\pi}{3}} \\\\\n\t\t\t& =e^{-i \\frac{2 \\pi}{3}} \\\\ &=\\cos \\left(-\\frac{2 \\pi}{3}\\right)+i \\sin \\left(-\\frac{2 \\pi}{3}\\right) \\\\\n\t\t\t& =-\\frac{1}{2}-\\frac{i \\sqrt{3}}{2}\n\t\t\\end{align*}$$"
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "value": "$\\frac{i}{(1+i \\sqrt{2})^2}$"
    },
    {
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": "$$\\begin{align*}\n\t\t\t\\frac{i}{(1+i \\sqrt{2})^2} & =\\frac{i}{1^2+2 \\sqrt{2} i+(i \\sqrt{2})^2}\\\\ &=\\frac{i}{1-2+2 \\sqrt{2} i}=\\frac{i}{-1+2 \\sqrt{2} i}\\\\ &=\\frac{i(-1-2 \\sqrt{2} i)}{(-1+2 \\sqrt{2} i)(-1-2 \\sqrt{2} i)} \\\\\n\t\t\t& =\\frac{2 \\sqrt{2}-i}{(1+8)} \\\\ &=\\frac{2 \\sqrt{2}}{9}-\\frac{i}{9}\n\t\t\\end{align*}$$"
    }
  ]
